msgid ""
"Beneath that, Odoo asks the former subscriber to :guilabel:`Please let us "
"know why you updated your subscription`, and the user can proceed to choose "
"the appropriate opt-out reason from a series of options presented to them."
msgstr ""
"Nedenfor beder Odoo den tidligere abonnent om at :guilabel:`fortælle os, "
"hvorfor du har opdateret dit abonnement`, og brugeren kan fortsætte med at "
"vælge den passende afmeldingsårsag fra en række muligheder, der præsenteres "
"for dem."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:53
msgid ""
"The opt-out answer options can be created and modified by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Email Marketing app --> Configuration --> Optout Reasons`."
msgstr ""
"Mulighederne for afmeldingsårsager kan oprettes og ændres ved at navigere "
"til :menuselection:`E-mailmarketing-app --> Konfiguration --> "
