msgstr "Visning af siden med sortlistede e-mailadresser i Odoo E-mailmarketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing/unsubscriptions.rst:92
msgid ""
"When a blacklisted record is selected from this list, Odoo reveals a "
"separate page with the recipient's contact information, along with the "
"provided :guilabel:`Reason` why they chose to blacklist themselves."
msgstr ""
"Når en sortlistet post vælges fra denne liste, viser Odoo en separat side "
"med modtagerens kontaktoplysninger sammen med den angivne :guilabel:`Årsag` "
"til, hvorfor de valgte at sortliste sig selv."

