#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_analysis.rst:64
msgid ":guilabel:`On webhook`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ved webhook`"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_analysis.rst:66
msgid ""
"Other options may appear based on the :guilabel:`Model` selected. For "
"example if the :guilabel:`Calendar Event` model is selected, then the "
"following options appear in addition to those above:"
msgstr ""
"Andre muligheder kan vises baseret på den valgte :guilabel:`Model`. Hvis "
"f.eks. modellen :guilabel:`Kalender Arrangement` vælges, vises følgende "
"muligheder ud over ovenstående:"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_analysis.rst:70
msgid ":guilabel:`Email Events`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`E-mail-arrangementer`"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_analysis.rst:72
msgid ":guilabel:`On incoming message`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ved indgående besked`"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_analysis.rst:73
msgid ":guilabel:`On outgoing message`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ved udgående besked`"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_analysis.rst:75
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Before Update Domain` field, set a condition to be met "
"before updating the record. Click :guilabel:`Edit Domain` to set record "
"parameters."
msgstr ""
"Under feltet :guilabel:`Domæne før opdatering` indstilles en betingelse, der "
"skal være opfyldt, før posten opdateres. Klik på :guilabel:`Rediger domæne` "
"for at indstille postparametre."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_analysis.rst:78
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Actions To Do` tab, select :guilabel:`Add an action`. "
"Next, in the resulting :guilabel:`Create Actions` pop-up window, "
"select :guilabel:`Send SMS`, and set the :guilabel:`Allowed "
"Groups`. :guilabel:`Allowed Groups` are the access rights groups that are "
"allowed to execute this rule. Leave the field empty to allow all groups. See "
"this documentation: :ref:`access-rights/groups`."
msgstr ""
"Under fanen :guilabel:`Handlinger at udføre` vælges :guilabel:`Tilføj en "
"handling`. Vælg derefter :guilabel:`Send SMS` i pop op-vinduet "
":guilabel:`Opret handlinger`, og angiv :guilabel:`Tilladte grupper`. "
":guilabel:`Tilladte grupper` er de adgangsrettighedsgrupper, der har "
"tilladelse til at udføre denne regel. Lad feltet være tomt for at tillade "
"alle grupper. Se denne dokumentation: :ref:`access-rights/groups`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_analysis.rst:84
msgid ""
"Next, set the :guilabel:`SMS Template` and choose whether the SMS message "
"should be logged as a note, by making a selection in the drop-down "
"menu: :guilabel:`Send SMS as`. Click :guilabel:`Save and Close` to save the "
"changes to this new action."
msgstr ""
"Indstil derefter :guilabel:`SMS-skabelon`, og vælg om SMS-beskeden skal "
"logges som en note ved at foretage et valg i rullemenuen: :guilabel:`Send "
"SMS som`. Klik på :guilabel:`Gem og luk` for at gemme ændringerne til denne "
"nye handling."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_analysis.rst:None
msgid ""
"Automation rule template with rule to do, SMS template and log as note "
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Automatiseringsregelskabelon med regel at udføre, SMS-skabelon og log som "
"note fremhævet."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_analysis.rst:92
msgid ""
"Add any necessary notes under the :guilabel:`Notes` tab. Finally, navigate "
"away from the completed automation rule, or manually save (by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`☁️ (cloud)` icon), to implement the change."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj eventuelle nødvendige noter under fanen :guilabel:`Noter`. Naviger "
"endelig væk fra den færdige automatiseringsregel, eller gem manuelt (ved at "
"klikke på ikonet :guilabel:`☁️ (sky)`) for at implementere ændringen."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:3
msgid "Basic SMS setup"
msgstr "Grundlæggende SMS-opsætning"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo **SMS Marketing** allows users to send SMS text messages in one of two "
"ways:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo **SMS Marketing** giver brugere mulighed for at sende SMS-tekstbeskeder "
"på en af to måder:"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:7
msgid "Using Odoo's out-of-the-box :abbr:`IAP (In-app purchases)` service."
msgstr "Ved at bruge Odoos indbyggede :abbr:`IAP (in-app køb)`-tjeneste."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:8
msgid "Using a third-party :doc:`Twilio integration <twilio>`."
msgstr "Ved at bruge en tredjepartsintegration med :doc:`Twilio <twilio>`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:10
msgid ""
"The following documentation covers the configuration process for users to "
"send SMS messages using Odoo :abbr:`IAP (In-app purchases)`."
msgstr ""
"Følgende dokumentation dækker konfigurationsprocessen for brugere, der skal "
"sende SMS-beskeder ved hjælp af Odoo :abbr:`IAP (in-app køb)`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:14
msgid "Built-in SMS configuration"
msgstr "Indbygget SMS-konfiguration"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:16
msgid ""
"In Odoo, SMS text messaging is an :abbr:`IAP (In-app purchases)` service "
"that sends messages directly from the database using prepaid :ref:`IAP "
"credits <in_app_purchase/credits>`."
msgstr ""
"I Odoo er SMS-tekstbeskeder en :abbr:`IAP (in-app køb)`-tjeneste, der sender "
"beskeder direkte fra databasen ved hjælp af forudbetalte :ref:`IAP-kreditter "
"<in_app_purchase/credits>`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:19
msgid ""
"Each time a user sends an SMS message in Odoo, credits are deducted from the "
"database's IAP account. The pricing of the message depends on the "
"destination and number of characters in the message. See `Odoo SMS - FAQ "
"<https://iap-services.odoo.com/iap/sms/pricing#sms_faq_01>`_ for a list of "
"prices per country."
msgstr ""
"Hver gang en bruger sender en SMS-besked i Odoo, trækkes der kreditter fra "
"databasens IAP-konto. Prisen på beskeden afhænger af destinationen og "
"antallet af tegn i beskeden. Se `Odoo SMS - FAQ <https://iap-"
"services.odoo.com/iap/sms/pricing#sms_faq_01>`_ for en liste over priser pr. "
"land."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:24
msgid ""
"The built-in SMS option allows users to send messages immediately with "
"minimal configuration. The following steps explain how to set it up and use "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Den indbyggede SMS-mulighed giver brugere mulighed for at sende beskeder med "
"det samme med minimal konfiguration. Følgende trin forklarer, hvordan den "
"opsættes og bruges."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:28
msgid ""
"Users needing more extensive configuration or that must adhere to stricter "
"compliance regulations (e.g., in the US or Canada) may use Twilio instead, "
"although pricing may vary from the built-in option."
msgstr ""
"Brugere, der har brug for mere omfattende konfiguration, eller som skal "
"overholde strengere overholdelsesregler (f.eks. i USA eller Canada), kan "
"bruge Twilio i stedet, selvom priserne kan variere fra den indbyggede "
"mulighed."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:33
msgid "Register SMS account"
msgstr "Registrer SMS-konto"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:35
msgid ""
"Before SMS messages can be sent, an SMS account must be registered through "
"the :abbr:`IAP (In-app-purchases)` service and purchase the required credits "
"needed to send SMS messages."
msgstr ""
"Før SMS-beskeder kan sendes, skal en SMS-konto registreres gennem :abbr:`IAP "
"(in-app køb)`-tjenesten og købe de nødvendige kreditter, der er nødvendige "
"for at sende SMS-beskeder."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:38
msgid ""
"To register an SMS account, open the **Settings** app and scroll to the "
"*Contacts* section. Under the :guilabel:`Send SMS` field, make sure "
"the :guilabel:`Send via Odoo` option is selected. Then, click :icon:`oi-"
"arrow-right` :guilabel:`Manage Service & Buy Credits` to open the SMS "
"account settings page."
msgstr ""
"For at registrere en SMS-konto skal du åbne appen **Indstillinger** og rulle "
"ned til sektionen *Adressebog*. Under feltet :guilabel:`Send SMS` skal du "
"sikre dig, at muligheden :guilabel:`Send via Odoo` er valgt. Klik derefter "
"på :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Administrer tjeneste og køb kreditter` "
"for at åbne siden med SMS-kontoindstillinger."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:44
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Send via Odoo` only appears if the **Twilio** module is "
"installed. An additional :guilabel:`Send via Twilio` option also appears."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Send via Odoo` vises kun, hvis **Twilio**-modulet er installeret. "
"En yderligere mulighed :guilabel:`Send via Twilio` vises også."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:None
msgid "Settings page for setting up an SMS account in Odoo."
msgstr "Indstillingsside til opsætning af en SMS-konto i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:50
msgid ""
"For first-time users, a highlighted warning message appears at the top of "
"the page, indicating the account is not registered. Click :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Register` next to the message to register an SMS account, "
"and a *Register Account* pop-up window appears. Enter a mobile phone number "
"to receive an SMS verification code. Once entered, click :guilabel:`Send "
"verification code`."
msgstr ""
"For førstegangbrugere vises en fremhævet advarselsbesked øverst på siden, "
"der angiver, at kontoen ikke er registreret. Klik på :icon:`oi-arrow-right` "
":guilabel:`Registrer` ved siden af beskeden for at registrere en SMS-konto, "
"og et pop op-vindue *Registrer konto* vises. Indtast et mobiltelefonnummer "
"for at modtage en SMS-verifikationskode. Når det er indtastet, skal du "
"klikke på :guilabel:`Send verifikationskode`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:55
msgid ""
"After receiving the code, enter it in the :guilabel:`Verification Code` "
"field. Then, click :guilabel:`Register` to continue."
msgstr ""
"Efter at have modtaget koden skal du indtaste den i feltet "
":guilabel:`Verifikationskode`. Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Registrer` for at "
"fortsætte."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:58
msgid ""
"On the *Choose your sender name* pop-up window, enter a sender name between "
"3 and 11 alphanumeric characters. Once set, this name **cannot** be modified."
msgstr ""
"I pop op-vinduet *Vælg dit afsendernavn* skal du indtaste et afsendernavn på "
"mellem 3 og 11 alfanumeriske tegn. Når det er angivet, **kan** dette navn "
"**ikke** ændres."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:61
msgid ""
"Once entered, click :guilabel:`Set sender name`. Alternatively, "
"click :guilabel:`Skip for now` to continue without setting a sender name."
msgstr ""
"Når den er indtastet, klik på :guilabel:`Angiv afsendernavn`. Alternativt "
"kan du klikke på :guilabel:`Spring over for nu` for at fortsætte uden at "
"angive et afsendernavn."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:65
msgid ""
"If a sender name is not set, SMS messages are sent from a short code. "
"A :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Set Sender Name` option appears on the "
"SMS account settings page for the user to configure when desired."
msgstr ""
"Hvis et afsendernavn ikke er angivet, sendes SMS-beskeder fra en kort kode. "
"En :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Angiv afsendernavn` mulighed vises på "
"SMS-kontoindstillingssiden, så brugeren kan konfigurere det, når det ønskes."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:70
msgid "Purchase credits"
msgstr "Køb kreditter"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:72
msgid ""
"To purchase credits, open the **Settings** app and scroll to the *Contacts* "
"section. Ensure that :guilabel:`Send via Odoo` is selected under *Send SMS*, "
"then click :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Manage Service & Buy Credits`."
msgstr ""
"For at købe kreditter skal du åbne appen **Indstillinger** og scrolle ned "
"til afsnittet *Adressebog*. Sørg for, at :guilabel:`Send via Odoo` er valgt "
"under *Send SMS*, og klik derefter på :icon:`oi-arrow-right` "
":guilabel:`Administrer tjeneste & køb kreditter`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:76
msgid ""
"On the SMS account settings page, click :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Buy Credit` next to the :guilabel:`Balance` field."
msgstr ""
"På SMS-kontoindstillingssiden skal du klikke på :icon:`oi-arrow-right` "
":guilabel:`Køb kredit` ved siden af feltet :guilabel:`Saldo`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:79
msgid ""
"The user is then directed to a :guilabel:`Buy credits for SMS` page on "
"the :abbr:`IAP (In-app purchases)` portal, displaying various credit packs "
"available for purchase."
msgstr ""
"Brugeren dirigeres derefter til en :guilabel:`Køb kreditter til SMS` side på "
":abbr:`IAP (In-app-køb)` portalen, der viser forskellige kreditpakker "
"tilgængelige til køb."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:None
msgid "Buy SMS Credits page in the Odoo IAP Portal."
msgstr "Køb SMS-kreditter side i Odoo IAP-portalen."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:85
msgid ""
"To purchase credits, click :guilabel:`Buy` under the desired credit pack. "
"Then, follow the prompts on the Odoo payment page to finalize the order."
msgstr ""
"For at købe kreditter skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Køb` under den ønskede "
"kreditpakke. Følg derefter instruktionerne på Odoo-betalingssiden for at "
"afslutte ordren."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:89
msgid ""
"The SMS account settings page can also be accessed by navigating to the "
"**Settings** app, scrolling to the *Contacts* section, then "
"clicking :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`View My Services` under *Odoo "
"IAP*."
msgstr ""
"SMS-kontoindstillingssiden kan også tilgås ved at navigere til appen "
"**Indstillinger**, scrolle ned til afsnittet *Adressebog* og derefter klikke "
"på :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Se mine tjenester` under *Odoo IAP*."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:93
msgid ""
"On the resulting dashboard of IAP accounts in the database, "
"select :guilabel:`SMS` to open the SMS account settings page."
msgstr ""
"På det resulterende dashboard over IAP-konti i databasen skal du vælge "
":guilabel:`SMS` for at åbne SMS-kontoindstillingssiden."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:97
msgid "Testing"
msgstr "Test"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:99
msgid ""
"After configuration, users can test that the SMS service works by sending "
"a :ref:`test marketing campaign message <sms_marketing/sms_configuration/"
"testing/campaign-test>` or by sending an SMS :ref:`directly from a contact "
"form <sms_marketing/sms_configuration/testing/contact-test>`."
msgstr ""
"Efter konfiguration kan brugere teste, at SMS-tjenesten virker ved at sende "
"en :ref:`testbesked til marketingkampagne <sms_marketing/sms_configuration/"
"testing/campaign-test>` eller ved at sende en SMS :ref:`direkte fra en "
"kontaktformular <sms_marketing/sms_configuration/testing/contact-test>`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:106
msgid "Marketing campaign test message"
msgstr "Testbesked til marketingkampagne"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:108
msgid ""
"To send a test SMS message, open the **SMS Marketing** app. Select an "
"existing SMS marketing campaign or :doc:`create a new one "
"<marketing_campaigns>`."
msgstr ""
"For at sende en test-SMS-besked skal du åbne appen **SMS Marketing**. Vælg "
"en eksisterende SMS-marketingkampagne eller :doc:`opret en ny "
"<marketing_campaigns>`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:111
msgid ""
"Ensure there is text in the :guilabel:`SMS Content` tab of the campaign "
"form, then click :guilabel:`Test`. A *Test Mailing* pop-up window appears."
msgstr ""
"Sørg for, at der er tekst i fanen :guilabel:`SMS-indhold` på "
"kampagneformularen, og klik derefter på :guilabel:`Test`. Et pop-up-vindue "
"*Testudsendelse* vises."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:None
msgid "View of an SMS test in Odoo SMS Marketing."
msgstr "Visning af en SMS-test i Odoo SMS Marketing."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:117
msgid ""
"Enter a test mobile number, then click :guilabel:`Send Test`. The user can "
"then verify that an SMS message has been sent."
msgstr ""
"Indtast et testmobilnummer, og klik derefter på :guilabel:`Send test`. "
"Brugeren kan derefter verificere, at en SMS-besked er blevet sendt."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:121
msgid ""
"In the *Settings* tab of the campaign form, the user can choose to include "
"an opt-out link in the SMS message. Note that this link counts towards the "
"pricing of the message."
msgstr ""
"Under fanen *Indstillinger* på kampagneformularen kan brugeren vælge at "
"inkludere et frameldingslink i SMS-beskeden. Bemærk, at dette link tæller "
"med i prisfastsættelsen af beskeden."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:127
msgid "Contact form test message"
msgstr "Testbesked fra kontaktformular"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:129
msgid ""
"Alternatively, users can also test SMS messages by directly sending a real "
"message through a contact form. To do this, open the **Contacts** app and "
"select a contact record. Click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` icon "
"and select :guilabel:`Send SMS`. A *Send SMS* pop-up window appears."
msgstr ""
"Alternativt kan brugere også teste SMS-beskeder ved direkte at sende en "
"rigtig besked gennem en kontaktformular. For at gøre dette skal du åbne "
"appen **Adressebog** og vælge en kontaktpost. Klik på ikonet :icon:`fa-cog` "
":guilabel:`(tandhjul)` og vælg :guilabel:`Send SMS`. Et pop-up-vindue *Send "
"SMS* vises."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:133
msgid "Enter a message in the text box, then click :guilabel:`Send`."
msgstr "Indtast en besked i tekstfeltet, og klik derefter på :guilabel:`Send`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:135
msgid ""
"The user can then verify that an SMS message has been sent in the chatter "
"next to the contact form."
msgstr ""
"Brugeren kan derefter verificere, at en SMS-besked er blevet sendt i "
"chatteren ved siden af kontaktformularen."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:138
msgid ":doc:`twilio`"
msgstr ":doc:`twilio`"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/sms_configuration.rst:139
msgid ":doc:`pricing_and_faq`"
msgstr ":doc:`pricing_and_faq`"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:4
msgid "SMS via Twilio"
msgstr "SMS via Twilio"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:7
msgid "What is Twilio"
msgstr "Hvad er Twilio"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:9
msgid ""
"Twilio is a third-party provider that enables you to send SMS messages to "
"your clients. Odoo provides an easy way to use this service within your Odoo "
"apps."
msgstr ""
"Twilio je poskytovatel třetí strany, který vám umožňuje posílat SMS zprávy "
"vašim klientům. Odoo poskytuje jednoduchý způsob, jak tuto službu používat v "
"rámci vašich aplikací Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:13
msgid "Why would I need it?"
msgstr "Proč bych to potřeboval?"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:15
msgid ""
"Although Odoo already comes with an out-of-the-box (IAP) solution for SMS "
"messages, it might not work in some countries with stricter legal "
"requirements. Currently, Odoo registers itself when possible to avoid extra "
"setup for its customers, however in some countries that is not enough and "
"the client itself must do it. This can be done through Twilio."
msgstr ""
"Přestože Odoo již přichází s готовым (IAP) řešením pro SMS zprávy, nemusí "
"fungovat v některých zemích s přísnějšími právními požadavky. V současné "
"době se Odoo registruje samo, když je to možné, aby se vyhnulo dalšímu "
"nastavení pro své zákazníky, avšak v některých zemích to nestačí a musí to "
"udělat sám klient. To lze provést prostřednictvím Twilio."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:21
msgid "Setup your Twilio account"
msgstr "Nastavit účet Twilio"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:23
msgid ""
"By creating a Twilio account, you will be able to create a virtual phone "
"number from which you will be able to send SMS messages. These cost credits "
"that are to be bought on Twilio, not Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Vytvořením účtu Twilio budete moci vytvořit virtuální telefonní číslo, ze "
"kterého budete moci posílat SMS zprávy. Tyto stojí kredity, které je třeba "
"koupit na Twilio, ne v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:26
msgid "Go to `Twilio <https://www.twilio.com>`_"
msgstr "Přejděte na `Twilio <https://www.twilio.com>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:27
msgid "Sign up and create a Twilio account"
msgstr "Zaregistrujte se a vytvořte účet Twilio"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:28
msgid ""
"Within your Twilio account, you can create multiple accounts (e.g. one for "
"testing, one for each sub-company, etc.)"
msgstr ""
"V rámci svého účtu Twilio můžete vytvořit více účtů (např. jeden pro "
"testování, jeden pro každou podspolečnost atd.)"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:30
msgid "Create a new account"
msgstr "Vytvořit nový účet"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/sms_marketing/twilio.rst:32
